{"tid":1263212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 連尼住入一入黎唔該","createTime":"2019-06-28T05:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T01:02:02.000Z","uid":165485,"like":141,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"da77872436c4209beeec1c93663a416f7eb04ec3","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"要求最近既活動post都可以比番樓主改#1既內容<br />\n<br />\n因為好多時巴絲都追唔切post<br />\n又或者推得太快 可能搭轉車已經錯過左好多update<br />\n同時太多幾千正皮既post推晒上熱門<br />\n反而有好多即時活動post都唔係個個一開就睇到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以如果樓主可以改到內容 會令召集更有效率</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當然出活動post既樓主們要出post時更加負責任<br />\n但係經過咁多日既民意自決 我相信好多連登仔都比某d部隊更有紀律<br />\n雖然短暫違反左兩登一直以黎既傳統<br />\n但係為左香港既進步 希望連仔可以考慮一下<br />\n<br />\n最後當然唔係我自己一個人既提議就要話決定咁做<br />\n照舊公投<br />\n支持＝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對＝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b23a59231829f63219175a3c3ae7cc842375fc8","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"先投為快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97225ad52abeaead7d6b2fb30ee1ca67e69d35c","tid":1263212,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b23a59231829f63219175a3c3ae7cc842375fc8","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"先投為快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c8ce558e14b1b7135eaf09d4d2f18cc487e97d","tid":1263212,"uid":244332,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"建議edit完內容要加返記錄，好似fb edit完post俾人睇返改左d咩係有必要"},{"pid":"89ecf7eec45d7168996495470d14407066c47db7","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"另外有好多文宣都可以係一個post整合置頂<br />\n會方便好多巴絲打repost出去比人睇<br />\n未睇過既人都會一眼睇晒<br />\n雖然咁做都係搞到成個香討u汪咁<br />\n但係無可否認會大大提升效率"},{"pid":"5daf18ce5f7a8971b5d24341dffde904bbaf8767","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"唔止文宣<br />\n仲有好多黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罪證<br />\n都可以一眼睇晒<br />\n呢樣都好重要"},{"pid":"5f9fae28815aef51106d22ca2ce9e5e80116e4d8","tid":1263212,"uid":4875,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"如果有幾千正評 樓主突然改內容，咪姐係騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02dd920a8b98ec869b70f3d79e7a0122adce03cc","tid":1263212,"uid":36134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"強烈反對"},{"pid":"c69cc2d9bb37fa60ffe5090d312c76d4ab9cc76e","tid":1263212,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f9fae28815aef51106d22ca2ce9e5e80116e4d8","tid":1263212,"uid":4875,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"如果有幾千正評 樓主突然改內容，咪姐係騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"d1c53cd516ab089e05b9846ea4a0c475ca14a934","tid":1263212,"uid":189615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c69cc2d9bb37fa60ffe5090d312c76d4ab9cc76e","tid":1263212,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f9fae28815aef51106d22ca2ce9e5e80116e4d8","tid":1263212,"uid":4875,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"如果有幾千正評 樓主突然改內容，咪姐係騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"Yes"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"可加不可減呢？"},{"pid":"ad05b849fffd65d705663a40012884e17a8cd5c1","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":1,"dislike":1