性<br />\n唔係要求以後有呢個功能<br />\n但係呢段時間真係好需要呢d功能去update人群"},{"pid":"29e01607458261ecc9064e6c861b699b05889b2e","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"705e6d6a819a14812eba4aea7c48658d97c9bea2","tid":1263212,"uid":18639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"你講既依d算係大update黎 唔係短時間話加就加到既function<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"如果係咁都無辦法<br />\n但係下次有活動就會方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4b1844d98d1ce30258b369c2647e2fe37f2aa1","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63887014616ed157783468b92c483f375085836","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a1977feec2774e1342eee96df520a6fd89375f","tid":1263212,"uid":165485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c446fc12a8a830c6d6273c3c016f48ba16ac2e","tid":1263212,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T08:17:13.000Z","msg":"幫pish"}]}